-# Locals: subject_name, subject_kind (:assignment or :position)
- subject_name = local_assigns.fetch(:subject_name)
- subject_kind = local_assigns.fetch(:subject_kind)
- is_assignment = subject_kind.to_sym == :assignment
- subject_label = is_assignment ? "assignment" : "position"
- change_section_title = "Change Milestone Requirement"
- add_section_title = "Add additional Milestone Requirements"
- save_label = is_assignment ? "Save Ability Milestones" : "Save Direct Milestone Requirements"

.alert.alert-light.border.mb-0
  %h3.fw-semibold.mb-2 Goal of this page
  %p.mb-3
    - if is_assignment
      Define which Abilities—and at which Milestone level—someone needs to do the job of
      %strong= subject_name
      well.
    - else
      Set direct Ability Milestone requirements on the
      %strong= subject_name
      position (in addition to requirements that come through its Assignments).

  %h3.fw-semibold.mb-2 Context
  = render "shared/maap/definition"

  %h3.fw-semibold.mb-2 Specifics of this page
  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 The two sections
  %ul.mb-3
    %li
      %strong= "#{change_section_title}:"
      Abilities already required for this #{subject_label}. Change the Milestone level, or choose
      %em No Association
      to remove a requirement.
    %li
      %strong= "#{add_section_title}:"
      Abilities not yet required. Collapsed by default when requirements already exist; expanded when this #{subject_label} has none yet. Use search to filter by Ability name or department.

  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 How to set a Milestone
  %p.mb-2
    Each row shows the department, Ability name, and Milestone buttons
    %span.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-primary.me-1 1
    through
    %span.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-primary.mx-1 5
    plus
    %span.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary.ms-1
      %em No Association
    \.
    Hover a Milestone button for a popover titled like
    %em Milestone 3 (Expert) for {Ability}
    with that Milestone’s description.
  %p.mb-3
    Example: for Ability
    %strong Coaching
    , choosing
    %span.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-primary 2
    means this #{subject_label} requires
    %strong Advanced
    Coaching (Milestone 2).

  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 Saving
  %p.mb-0
    Click
    %strong= save_label
    when you are done. Unsaved Milestone picks in the add section stay local until you save; use
    %em No Association
    to clear a mistaken pick without refreshing.
